Task 8 - Employee Management (Spring Core)

This project demonstrates a simple Employee Management module using Spring Core concepts like Inversion of Control (IoC) and Dependency Injection (DI).

Features:

Spring Core (no Spring Boot)
Use of @Component and @Autowired annotations
Demonstrates IoC and Dependency Injection
BeanFactory used to manage beans
Employee data stored in memory
Components:

Employee class to store employee details
Service class to manage employee operations
Configuration class for Spring setup
Functionality:

Add employee
View employee details
Store data temporarily (in-memory)
Tools Used:

Java
Spring Core
Maven
